Cyber Claw/Quickstrike:




Cyber Claw studied the cooridnates for a few seconds, then nodded. 
She left the room.



Quickstrike's optics went heavy. Restless with pacing and being wary 
of Hell Beast, Megatron, and Black Arachnia's news were begining to 
catch up with him. He needed time to rest.

"Ah'll be in mah quarters, sugar-bot." he said to Black Arachnia, and 
left her side. "Hollar if ya need anythin'." he said before he left 
the room. He rolled his dislocated shoulder with a grimace while he 
walked down the corridors. He would have to try and fix it himself 
when he got to his quarters. He could try and hit it against the 
frame of the door. That might work.
